To get Infoblox to properly distribute IPs you must add the following "Custom properties" at the project level

Name: Infoblox.IPAM.Network.dnsView
Value: Internal Network

The value needs to match the default name of ip/dns zone as listed in Infoblox ... Internal Network should be the default.



Integrations > Infoblox > Key / Value pair settings

Infoblox.IPAM.DisableCertificateCheck : True
Infoblox.IPAM.WAPIVersion : 2.7
Infoblox.IPAM.HTTPTimeout : 30
Infoblox.IPAM.LogApiCallsAsInfo : False
Infoblox.IPAM.NetworkContainerFiler : -
Infoblox.IPAM.NetworkFiler : *DeviceType=Server
Infoblox.IPAM.RangeFiler : *FS_Site=ignore
Infoblox.IPAM.Network.dnsView : HOMELAB
